The paper deals with a secure wireless code dissemination mechanism for Computational Radio Frequency Identification (CRFID) devices, which involves hardware security primitives and firmware updates. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), machine learning (cs.LG), and systems and control (cs.SY).
